Y 41 — also in van Roosmalen’s home country of Holland — with the Dutchman taking home a controversial, majority-decision victory." type="episode" contentRating="PG-13" duration="9070000" grandparentArt="https://dki01q1l7yn3y.cloudfront.net/thumbnails-platform-prod/assets/cs::content::shows/11056-13104/22644294-default_v1.jpeg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/6489b1f1782e547231bd91c4" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/6489b1f1782e547231bd91c4" grandparentRatingKey="6489b1f1782e547231bd91c4" grandparentThumb="https://provider-static.plex.tv/epg/cms/production/e82ff7c4-015e-440d-a8df-d960efc5d3f8/GLORY_2000x3000_Nicholas_Olsen.jpg" grandparentTitle="GLORY Kickboxing" grandparentType="show" index="10" originallyAvailableAt="2018-09-29T00:00:23Z" parentIndex="7" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://dki01q1l7yn3y.cloudfront.net/thumbnails-platform-prod/assets/cs::content::episodemeta/15374-17422/31486591-default_v1.jpg" title="GLORY 59 Amsterdam" userState="0" year="2018"><Image alt="GLORY 59 Amsterdam" type="coverArt" url="https://dki01q1l7yn3y.cloudfront.net/thumbnails-platform-prod/assets/cs::content::shows/11056-13104/22644294-default_v1.jpeg"/><Image alt="GLORY 59 Amsterdam" type="coverPoster" url="https://provider-static.plex.tv/epg/cms/production/e82ff7c4-015e-440d-a8df-d960efc5d3f8/GLORY_2000x3000_Nicholas_Olsen.jpg"/><Image alt="GLORY 59 Amsterdam" type="snapshot" url="https://dki01q1l7yn3y.cloudfront.net/thumbnails-platform-prod/assets/cs::content::episodemeta/15374-17422/31486591-default_v1.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" id="620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" ratingKey="genre_620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" slug="sports" tag="Sports" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1773992584" duration="9070000" endsAt="1774001654" id="69b5fe006a7d22e65743c826" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1774044985" duration="9070000" endsA